data.meta_description: Daniel Wass profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
Daniel Wass is 35 years old (May 31, 1989), 181 cm tall and plays for Brøndby IF.

Daniel Wass prefers to play with right foot. His jersey number is 10.

Daniel Wass career statistics, match ratings, heatmap and goals are available on Sofascore for current and previous seasons. Last player match was Lyngby - Brøndby IF (0 - 2) and Daniel Wass received 8.1 Sofascore rating.

Brøndby IF is playing their next match on Aug 8, 2024, 5:00:00 PM UTC against Brøndby IF - Legia Warszawa in UEFA Conference League.

If Daniel Wass is going to be in Brøndby IF lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Daniel Wass plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Daniel Wass football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Daniel Wass played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
